('72636','25196','5','Idyllic hotel rural near Manacor'),
('72637','25197','5','This hotel is one of the most idyllic country hotels in Mallorca and is located just a few kilometers from Manacor, nestled in a beautiful, quiet and hilly countryside, surrounded only by pure nature.\r\nThe hotel was created in 1995 from a former 300 years old country house and sits on a plot of approximately 33,000 m². It has been tastefully updated with typical Mallorcan materials. The large Mediterranean garden and the swimming pool (16m x 8m) invite to relax.\r\nThe hotel is run by the owner and is in excellent condition without any backlog in repairs. There are 3 junior suites, 9 double rooms and 1 single room. Further features include a kitchen, a reception office, breakfast room (restaurant) with fireplace lounge, terraces and a covered pool bar. An oil central heating provides for a comfortable room temperature in wintertime. It is possible to keep horses. The hotel could open all year-round.'),
